---
description: Documentation claim hygiene
globs:
  - README.md
  - docs/**/*.md
---

- Separate confirmed behavior, inference, and future work.
- When capability claims change, update `docs/references.md` in the same edit.
- Use exact, low-drama wording for unproven areas: "not yet proven", "not documented here", or "left opt-in".
- Avoid importing parity language from other repositories unless a specific Cursor surface truly matches.
